00:05:57,320 --> 00:06:00,520
 Waiting isn't just about sitting around doing nothing.

131
00:06:00,520 --> 00:06:04,720
 It's a posture of hope and expectation.

132
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:07,240
 The early believers didn't wait passively.

133
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:10,800
 They trusted in Jesus' promise and the Holy Spirit

134
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:13,480
 and their waiting was filled with purpose.

135
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:14,400
 And then last week,

136
00:06:14,400 --> 00:06:17,680
 Pastor John spoke about what it means to,

137
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:20,960
 to remember the word, receive, thank you,

138
00:06:20,960 --> 00:06:22,760
 to what it means to receive.

139
00:06:22,760 --> 00:06:25,080
 The waiting was finally over.

