00:06:25,080 --> 00:06:27,960
 Through Christ, God sent us the Holy Spirit,

141
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:30,560
 not just to gather in the upper room,

142
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,920
 but as a gift for everyone,

143
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:35,280
 men and women, young and old,

144
00:06:35,280 --> 00:06:37,440
 people from every nation.

145
00:06:37,440 --> 00:06:39,240
 It's a gift for all.

146
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:42,240
 And today, we're gonna talk about what it means

147
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:45,840
 to be empowered by the Holy Spirit.

148
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:48,560
 As the theologian, Gordon Fee, has said,

149
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:51,800
 "The gift of the Spirit is not given

