00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:56,560
 "a private spiritual experience,

152
00:06:56,560 --> 00:06:59,200
 "but so that they may participate

153
00:06:59,200 --> 00:07:01,600
 "in the life and mission of the church

154
00:07:01,600 --> 00:07:04,200
 "as the new people of God."

155
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:08,120
 There is a purpose and mission behind this gift.

156
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:11,720
 There is a purpose and mission behind this gift.

157
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:14,120
 The Holy Spirit empowers us

158
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:18,080
 for what God is calling us to do.

159
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:21,600
 We're not left alone to face this daunting task.

160
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:25,080
 We are empowered together by the Spirit

161
00:07:25,080 --> 00:07:27,600
 to live out God's mission in the world.

162
00:07:27,600 --> 00:07:30,600
 But what is our mission?

163
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:34,880
 As Acts 1.8 says, before Jesus ascended to heaven,

164
00:07:34,880 --> 00:07:39,320
 He said, "You will, we will be His witness in Jerusalem

165
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:41,320
 "and in all Judea and Samaria,

166
00:07:41,320 --> 00:07:43,640
 "and to the ends of the world."

167
00:07:43,640 --> 00:07:46,080
 It was clear that the mission to the disciples

168
00:07:46,080 --> 00:07:48,400
 was to be Christ's witnesses,

169
00:07:48,400 --> 00:07:51,800
 not just in Jerusalem, but till the end of the world.

170
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:55,840
 But this mission wasn't just for them back then.

171
00:07:55,840 --> 00:07:57,040
 It was for us too.

172
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:59,280
 We are called to be Christ's witness today

173
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:01,600
 in our home, in our workplaces.

174
00:08:01,600 --> 00:08:04,520
 But what is a mission?

175
00:08:04,520 --> 00:08:07,240
 What does being a witness mean?

176
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:11,400
 When I was younger, I attended a local church

177
