 where every few months, all the community groups,

178
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:18,080
 everyone would go out to hand out gospel tracts.

179
00:08:18,080 --> 00:08:19,840
 Do you know what are gospel tracts?

180
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:22,200
 There they are.

181
00:08:22,200 --> 00:08:26,680
 They are small pamphlets that explain what the gospel is,

182
00:08:26,680 --> 00:08:28,520
 usually with a simple story.

183
00:08:28,520 --> 00:08:31,640
 It's very in your face, right?

184
00:08:31,640 --> 00:08:32,920
 They explain what the gospel is,

185
00:08:32,920 --> 00:08:35,520
 usually with a short story or Bible verse.

186
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:38,440
 We would stand around the parks and bus stops

187
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:40,240
 and wait for people.

188
00:08:40,240 --> 00:08:42,440
 Imagine that you were given out a bunch of these

189
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:44,920
 and you have to stand around bus stops.

190
00:08:44,920 --> 00:08:46,720
 And then when the people get off the bus

