00:11:15,520 --> 00:11:18,720
 for me, has always been at home.

255
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:21,880
 My parents, more than anyone, know my flaws.

256
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:25,560
 My laziness, my procrastination,

257
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:27,440
 and those rebellious moments.

258
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:30,240
