00:34:53,640 --> 00:34:56,960
 Let our lives be undeniable proof

877
00:34:56,960 --> 00:35:00,040
 that Jesus' victory is real,

878
00:35:00,040 --> 00:35:04,080
 that His Holy Spirit really does change everything.

