 I also went to church when I was really young.

890
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:52,040
 But when my father passed away,

891
00:35:52,040 --> 00:35:55,000
 it forced me to ask this question,

892
00:35:55,000 --> 00:35:57,560
 God, are you there for me?

893
00:35:57,560 --> 00:35:59,680
 And it made me realize that I don't really

894
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:01,400
 have a relationship with Jesus.

