00:36:54,880 --> 00:37:00,520
 I would like you to speak to Jesus.

910
00:37:00,520 --> 00:37:08,840
 He loves you.

911
00:37:11,080 --> 00:37:12,120
 And He wants to.

912
00:37:12,120 --> 00:37:15,800
 And He wants you to be honest with Him.

913
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:22,400
 And in this moment, if you know that you may not

914
00:37:22,400 --> 00:37:25,160
 have a relationship with Him, but you want to,

915
00:37:25,160 --> 00:37:27,960
 you want to receive this grace,

916
00:37:27,960 --> 00:37:29,680
 you want to receive this love,

917
00:37:29,680 --> 00:37:36,000
 you want to receive this abundant life that He promised,

918
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:40,680
 and you want to turn away from the old way of life

919
00:37:40,680 --> 00:37:43,240
 because that has not been working out for you.

920
00:37:43,240 --> 00:37:46,480
 You have tried, you have used your own effort,

921
00:37:46,480 --> 00:37:49,960
 your own way of living, and it did not work.

922
00:37:49,960 --> 00:37:52,440
 You were hurting yourself, you were hurting people

923
00:37:52,440 --> 00:37:56,080
 around you, and you did not have a relationship with Jesus.

924
00:37:56,080 --> 00:38:00,600
 I'd like you, just at your seat,

