00:38:50,840 --> 00:38:57,520
 If you are one of those people that you want to be empowered

938
00:38:57,520 --> 00:39:01,520
 by the Holy Spirit today to live out the victorious life,

939
00:39:01,520 --> 00:39:04,640
 the reality that Jesus is alive,

940
00:39:06,000 --> 00:39:07,800
 I would like you to open up your hand

941
00:39:07,800 --> 00:39:14,320
 and to receive this Holy Spirit that empowers you

942
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:18,440
 to live victoriously, to live differently.

943
00:39:33,320 --> 00:39:37,000
 Jesus, we thank you, because today,

944
00:39:37,000 --> 00:39:42,800
 someone here has made a decision to follow you.

