00:39:42,800 --> 00:39:46,920
 I pray that by your grace and your power,

946
00:39:46,920 --> 00:39:50,600
 that you are going to fill him up with the Holy Spirit

947
00:39:50,600 --> 00:39:55,160
 to empower him to turn from his old ways and to run to you.

948
00:39:55,160 --> 00:40:01,560
 I pray that as he make his decision to receive you,

949
00:40:02,560 --> 00:40:07,560
 that you will give him and honor him

