00:40:07,560 --> 00:40:11,040
 and know that you will give him an abundant life.

951
00:40:11,040 --> 00:40:14,880
 Thank you for dying for us on the cross.

952
00:40:14,880 --> 00:40:18,800
 Thank you for forgiving our sin.

